pulses.name: 20240902 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
02 Sep 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN): The most active source, involved in multiple attacks targeting vulnerabilities in NETGEAR and D-Link devices, as well as the Mozi botnet.
- India (IN): Notable for its involvement in attacks leveraging the Mozi botnet and exploiting vulnerabilities in multiple routers, including GPON devices.
- Egypt (EG): Active in various attacks, particularly utilizing the Mirai botnet and exploiting MVPower DVR vulnerabilities.
